OL,3,CBlack children 15% less likely to be
OL,4,Coffered diversion choice, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FThe highest rates are in Bromley
OL,8,F(66%), Bexley (65%) and Kingston Upon
OL,9,FThames (65%). Where as the lowest are
OL,10,Fin Haringey (43%), Lambeth (42%) and
OL,11,FHackney (41%).
OL,13,FOmarni has benefitted from diversion
OL,14,Fafter he was arrested for carrying
OL,15,FClass A drugs.
OL,17,FHe is now a mentor at United Borders.
OL,19,F"When I was younger, all I was focused
OL,20,Fon was having fun and trying to make
OL,21,Fmoney as well," he said.
